---
title: Beef Rump & Peppercorn Hollandaise Sauce with Fries & Tomato Salad
description: Peppercorns meets hollandaise, a wonder duo sauce swooping in to transform this beef steak dinner into something new. Serve
up with a side of fries to catch any leftover sauce.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
